vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting a Planned Development District for MU-3 Mixed Use District uses and a vehicle display, sales, and service use on property zoned an MU-3 Mixed Use District, on the north line of West Northwest Highway, east of Shady Trail
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval, subject to a development plan and staff’s recommended conditions
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval, subject to a development plan and conditions with changes
Z223-178(LG)
